<exercise id="fs-id1167660304292">
<problem id="fs-id1167660304294">
<para id="fs-id1167660123705">Which of the following is the enzyme that replaces the RNA nucleotides in a primer with DNA nucleotides?</para>
<list id="fs-id1167660389115" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>DNA polymerase III</item>
<item>DNA polymerase I</item>
<item>primase</item>
<item>helicase</item>
</list>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167662566987">
<para id="fs-id1167662553014">B</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1167662519418">
<problem id="fs-id1167660216554">
<para id="fs-id1167660292706">Which of the following is not involved in the initiation of replication?</para>
