<exercise id="fs-id1167660255832">
<problem id="fs-id1167660255835">
<para id="fs-id1167660206602">Unidirectional replication of a circular DNA molecule like a plasmid that involves nicking one DNA strand and displacing it while synthesizing a new strand is called ________.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167660206604">
<para id="fs-id1167662680479">rolling circle replication</para>
</solution>
